description: Eva loves her quaint new neighbourhood complete with tree lined streets and eager city professionals. The recently married couple down the road, Audrey and Henry, eagerly welcome her fresh face to their quite borough and after a month of casual hellos and easy chats about the best restaurants near by, Audrey invites Eva over for movie night. "Nothing special, just popcorn and horror flicks. Wear your sweats!" says Audrey with her unflappable bubbly charm. The popcorn is great, the company even better but the horror movies are too much for Eva. Though the short walk home would likely not involve zombies jumping out of the bushes, she is just too scared to make the walk. Audrey rushes to set up the guest bedroom. The guest bedroom, however, has more to offer than just a comfy bed and when Eva is woken up to someone's mouth on her growing cock, she realizes her idyllic married friends have some dirty plans for the night.
